1.0.4 (2024-08-04)

        * Addressed Doxygen warnings about resolvable links to 'Error',
          'Info', and 'Debug' globals.

        * Addressed an issue in which unit tests could not be linked
          when the CppUnit package is / was not configured with
          pkg-config.

        * Handle GitHub Workflow Actions continuous integration (CI)
          on macOS with Apple Silicon (that is, arm64).

        * Updated nlbuild-autotools to 1.7.8.

        * Updated Doxygen configuration for Doxygen 1.11.0.

1.0.3 (2021-03-03)

        * Updated nlbuild-autotools to 1.6.14.

1.0.2 (2021-03-02)

	* Addressed macOS v. Linux portability issues.

1.0.1 (2021-03-02)

	* Addressed typos and style errors.

1.0 (2021-03-02)

	* First public release to Github.
